              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Links Section -->
        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-harmony mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13.828 10.172a4 4 0 00-5.656 0l-4 4a4 4 0 105.656 5.656l1.102-1.101m-.758-4.899a4 4 0 005.656 0l4-4a4 4 0 00-5.656-5.656l-1.1 1.1" />
            </svg>
            Links to Other Sites
          </h2>
          <div class="bg-harmony/5 border border-harmony/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              As a convenience to you, this Site may periodically provide links to third-party websites through links available on this Site, including websites of entities that are affiliated with Sing for Hope ("Third-Party Sites") where we feel it is appropriate. Our decision to link to a Third-Party Site is not an endorsement of the Content in that linked Third Party Site. <strong>WE ARE NOT RESPONSIBLE FOR THE CONTENT OF ANY THIRD-PARTY WEBSITE</strong>, and you should take precautions when accessing linked sites. If you decide to access linked Third-Party Sites, you do so at your own risk.
            </p>
